---
layout: 'default'
title: 'Home'
scripts: ['//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js']
---

.jumbotron
  .row
    .col-xs-10.col-sm-9.col-md-8.col-lg-6
      h1
        | Hi, I'm 
        a(href=site.links.about) John.

      t(render="markdown")
        | If you're reading this, chances are I handed you one of my cards,
        | or you followed [my LinkedIn profile][profile] here.
        | 
        | Welcome, and please [let me know][email] if you have questions
        | this site doesn't answer.
        | 
        | [email]: #{getEmail()}
        | [profile]: #{site.links.profile}
    .col-xs-2.col-sm-3.col-md-4.col-lg-6
      img.pull-right.img-responsive(src=getUrl("/img/profile/gravatar_large.jpg"))

.row
  .col-md-12
    p: a.twitter-timeline(href=getTwitterUrl(), data-widget-id=site.twitter.widgetId) Tweets by @#{site.twitter.id}
